This is based off the "Island Settlers" code.  Android 1.6 or higher is required.  It is here for the academic interests of fellow developers :)

This branch is a work-in-progress for porting the rendering engine to OpenGL ES.

To build it, you need the Android API version 8 and either Ant or the ADT Eclipse plugin.


